sequenceDiagram
    participant Sim as Stream Simulator
    participant API as FastAPI Router
    participant Buffer as InferenceService (Deque)
    participant Model as ML Production Model
    participant DB as SQLite DB
    participant WS as WebSocket Clients
    
    Sim->>API: POST /predict {"sensor_id": "T-01", "value": 75.4}
    API->>Buffer: Append to Rolling Window (MaxLen=65)
    
    alt Window Size < 65
        Buffer-->>API: Return Wait Status
        API-->>Sim: 202 Accepted (Warming Up)
    else Window Size == 65
        Buffer->>Buffer: Execute Feature Engineering (Numpy)
        Buffer-->>API: Return Feature Vector [1xN]
        API->>Model: predict(Feature Vector)
        Model-->>API: Return Anomaly Score (float)
        
        API->>API: Evaluate Score vs Model Threshold
        alt Score > Threshold
            API->>DB: INSERT INTO alerts (Critical)
            API->>WS: Broadcast Alert Event JSON
        end
        API->>WS: Broadcast Standard Telemetry JSON
        API-->>Sim: 200 OK (Processed)
    end
